#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/security-jwt.adoc:674
msgid "If the JWT token can not be injected, for example, if it is embedded in the service request payload or the service endpoint acquires it out of band, then one can use `JWTParser`: ``` import org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken; import io.smallrye.jwt.auth.principal.JWTParser; ...  @Inject JWTParser parser;"
